### Promotion API Examples
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/promotion

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Get all promotions with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/promotion?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get promotion by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/promotion/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get promotion by promo code
GET {{baseUrl}}/promotion/by-code/SALE10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get active promotions only
GET {{baseUrl}}/promotion/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Check if promo code exists
GET {{baseUrl}}/promotion/check-code/SALE10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Validate promotion
POST {{baseUrl}}/promotion/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SALE10",
  "orderAmount": 150000
}

### 7. Calculate discount amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/promotion/calculate-discount
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SALE10",
  "orderAmount": 150000
}

### 8. Create new promotion (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promotion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "description": "Summer sale 20% off",
  "discountType": 0,
  "discountValue": 20,
  "startDate": "2024-06-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-08-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 100000,
  "usageLimit": 1000
}

### 9. Create fixed discount promotion (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promotion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "FREESHIP50K",
  "description": "Free shipping 50k for orders over 300k",
  "discountType": 1,
  "discountValue": 50000,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 300000,
  "usageLimit": 500
}

### 10. Update promotion (Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/promotion/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoId": 1,
  "promoCode": "SALE10",
  "description": "Updated description for 10% sale",
  "discountType": 0,
  "discountValue": 10,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "minOrderAmount": 0,
  "usageLimit": 0,
  "usedCount": 0,
  "status": "active"
}

### 11. Delete promotion (Admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/promotion/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Deactivate expired promotions (Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/promotion/deactivate-expired
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notes:
### - DiscountType enum values: 0 = Percent, 1 = Fixed (auto-assigned by C#)
### - All dates should be in ISO 8601 format
### - Admin role required for create, update, delete operations
### - Staff and Admin roles can access read operations and validation
